6376516a","type":"paragraph","text":"同时总理指示：","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"eba030f157","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"768f0d80b0","type":"paragraph","text":"1．江西军区在“三支”、“两军”中犯了一些缺点错误，革命群众认为犯了方向路线性错误。你们应该很好解决。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"eba030f157","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"17fb6c4b04","type":"paragraph","text":"2．江西日报问题不要争论下去了，“江西日报”四个字可以暂时去掉，改出一个时期的新华电讯。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"eba030f157","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19ac6a9923","type":"paragraph","text":"3．不要把刘瑞森的问题看得太严重了。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"eba030f157","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"03ca8c3b68","type":"paragraph","text":"4．刘培善先作检查，军区那个检查，你们（指军区）自己研究。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"eba030f157","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}